==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|geostran dæg|lang=ang}}, equivalent to {{prefix|yester|day|lang=en}}; compounded from
* Old English {{term|geostran|lang=ang||yesterday}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*gestra-}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*dʰǵʰyes-}};
* Old English {{term|dæg|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*dagaz}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*dʰegʰ-||to burn}}

